{"tid":1100191,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[正評撐IU] 人間天使 IU捐一億反被追擊，逼使組織出面平反！","createTime":"2019-04-10T09:05:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T07:15:27.000Z","uid":34643,"like":53,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0d1ffc87fe66e82c23ae4843f26967edbb4f74cc","tid":1100191,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T09:05:41.000Z","msg":"一名韓國網民在討論區上載名為「IU可疑的捐贈」的文章，指IU在山火發生後，向專門幫助兒童的綠色雨傘兒童財團（譯名）捐一億韓元，質疑IU捐款的意圖。該網民講到，發生山火的地區完全沒有兒童，是「100%老人家」的地區，居民主要是從事農業的老人，因此不理解IU向兒童機構捐款的原因。文章在韓國網絡上迅速傳開，不少粉絲力撐出道11年來積極做善事的偶像，對於IU善心被懷疑而感到失望。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://t1.daumcdn.net/cfile/tistory/2179E94256C747C72E?original\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft1.daumcdn.net%2Fcfile%2Ftistory%2F2179E94256C747C72E%3Foriginal&h=3e2785a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然IU方面未有回應事件，可是<span style=\"color: red;\">綠色雨傘兒童財團就率先發聲明替IU平反。財團講到：「火災第二天組織到訪現場，了解受助兒童的情況，其中4個支援家庭的居住地，因是次山火完全被燒毀，其他家庭則正在避難所避難。」表示災區有救災的必要性。財團亦補充，IU的捐款並不只是用於綠色雨傘兒童財團，而是多個非牟利機構，包括IU母校東德女子高中發展基金支援等</span>，因此不希望網上不實的傳聞，令組織失去可信性，令更多兒童未有得到幫助。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CtpiBcRVYAAUhPF.jpg:orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCtpiBcRVYAAUhPF.jpg%3Aorig&h=abfe87d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CtpiBdyUAAAIWnf.jpg:orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCtpiBdyUAAAIWnf.jpg%3Aorig&h=b850a94a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2008年出道的IU來向人美心更美，多年來一直積極參與慈善活動，每當有災難性事件發生，她亦第一時間伸手援手。2011年時，IU舉動出道1004日紀念活動後，把當時的所有收益，包括音源及活動費用全數捐贈給正在培養歌手夢想的兒童。去年IU更以45億韓元（約3150萬港幣）土地和建築物，為母親及公司後輩開設個人辦公室和練習室，絕對是親力親為的天使。對於偶像善心被黑粉扭曲，粉絲都希望IU不要為事件影響。"},{"pid":"b898a47aad01c09555337bdc275185af8023adcc","tid":1100191,"uid":34676,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T09:06:54.000Z","msg":"其實韓國網民同中國網民真係世界兩大痴線組織"},{"pid":"8043547692031fba19d19a2bb4c17da2e025ac14","tid":1100191,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b898a47aad01c09555337bdc275185af8023adcc","tid":1100191,"uid":34676,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T09:06:54.000Z","msg":"其實韓國網民同中國網民真係世界兩大痴線組織"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T09:10:34.000Z","msg":"毒瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c65d1547477662ae59c78b461a9157a6be0a71","tid":1100191,"uid":7699,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T09:14:07.000Z","msg":"韓國不配有IU<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0750eed6c07ae3be360f96f713d20e6f0866aa96","tid":1100191,"uid":120093,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T09:18:00.000Z","msg":"捐錢都唔得？想屈佢避稅呀？"},{"pid":"2628e84dc4616f4fa3ff6e641637fdbeac2cf913","tid":1100191,"uid":76674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T09:24:56.000Z","msg":"韓國=人蔘字支那<br />\n批評人個班九成九都冇捐過錢做過善事"},{"pid":"00d28032cb4f06c9f907637935af4a070569890c","tid":1100191,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76c65d1547477662ae59c78b461a9157a6be0a71","tid":1100191,"uid":7699,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T09:14:07.000Z","msg":"韓國不配有IU<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T09:53:56.000Z","msg":"呢個真"},{"pid":"6cbb76b7c71b0176549ff0e9acee9a52be1673a6","tid":1100191,"uid":143093,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T10:03:25.000Z","msg":"性格好自然人都靚啲 相由身心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d72a2746cd6834e8fd79b913e1c6e9085adabd","tid":1100191,"uid":38784,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T10:05:25.000Z","msg":"劉在石捐得少過其他人 又比人屌 IU捐比某個組織 又比人屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj